After SMA has been successfully deployed and brought online, the next step is to configure a proper monitoring mechanism so that you can watch out for any potential issues with your worker nodes, pods, and services.
This document describes how to use Prometheus (which is an open source tool) to collect statistics information about CPU, memory, network I/O and disk IO for worker nodes, pods, and services in the SMA suite.
</p>
